    • addHeaderSource

      public GrafanaClientConfig addHeaderSource(Supplier<Map<String,String>> headerSource)
      Add a dynamic header source to be used for every new request. Each source provides a map of new headers. If key or value of any entry is null or empty, that entry is skipped. Otherwise, they are computed and added to every request anew.
      Parameters:
      headerSource - A source of new headers
      Returns:
      this GrafanaClientConfig, for method chaining
